  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for openssl-3",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for openssl-3 fixes the following issue:\n\nSecurity issues fixed:\n    \n- CVE-2026-28390: NULL pointer dereference during processing of a crafted CMS EnvelopedData message with\n  KeyTransportRecipientInfo (bsc#1261678).\n    \nOther updates and bugfixes:\n    \n- Enable MD2 in legacy provider (jsc#PED-15724).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
